member.summary:
Default refresh implementation.

for a single file will notify the tree to change the icon,
for more than one will cause a full tree refresh (might be expensive).

Looks up a localized string similar to Remove
{0}
from source control ?.

member.example:
Add the following namespace: xmlns:mynamespace="clr-namespace:MyNameSpace"

Create a static class returning a static property using this method:

namespace MyNameSpace
{

publib static class MyThemes
    {
        public static MyKey
        {
            get
            {
                return Themes.GetKey("MyKey");
            }
        }
    }
}

then you can use the key in a property using Dynamic Resource:
Foreground="{DynamicResource {x:Static MyNameSpace:MyThemes.MyKey}}"
